#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:2
#: a412cf285c544f549f023ad9a1030714
msgid "Taylor-Green Vortex (Convergence Study)"
msgstr "泰勒-格林涡（收敛性研究）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:4
#: 1d01c5fda48740338fae5cc8d1619222
msgid ""
"The Taylor-Green vortex is the canonical incompressible-flow benchmark with "
"a known exact solution: a periodic decaying vortex on the square :math:`[0, "
"2\\pi]^2` whose velocity and pressure can be written down in closed form. "
"The script ``examples/fluid/taylor_green/taylor_green.py`` uses it to drive "
"a quantitative **h-convergence study** of the transient Navier-Stokes solver"
" — the only example in :doc:`index` whose purpose is verification rather "
"than visualization."
msgstr ""
"泰勒-格林涡是具有已知精确解的经典不可压缩流动基准：在正方形 :math:`[0, 2\\pi]^2` "
"上的一个周期性衰减涡，其速度与压力都可写成闭式解。脚本 ``examples/fluid/taylor_green/taylor_green.py`` "
"用它来对瞬态纳维-斯托克斯求解器开展定量的 **h 收敛性研究**——这是 :doc:`index` 中唯一以验证而非可视化为目的的算例。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:15
#: 791f7b895d924109b37faacfb34faddb
msgid "Exact solution"
msgstr "精确解"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:17
#: 2217cb73d1b542a88f2fe37c73328973
msgid "For viscosity :math:`\\nu` and time :math:`t`,"
msgstr "对于黏度 :math:`\\nu` 与时间 :math:`t`\\ ，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:19
#: d1c022822aa34417985451c42279f52e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"u(x, y, t) &= -\\cos(x)\\, \\sin(y)\\, e^{-2\\nu t}, \\\\\n"
"v(x, y, t) &= \\phantom{-}\\sin(x)\\, \\cos(y)\\, e^{-2\\nu t}, \\\\\n"
"p(x, y, t) &= -\\tfrac14 \\bigl(\\cos(2x) + \\cos(2y)\\bigr)\\, e^{-4\\nu t}."
msgstr ""
"u(x, y, t) &= -\\cos(x)\\, \\sin(y)\\, e^{-2\\nu t}, \\\\\n"
"v(x, y, t) &= \\phantom{-}\\sin(x)\\, \\cos(y)\\, e^{-2\\nu t}, \\\\\n"
"p(x, y, t) &= -\\tfrac14 \\bigl(\\cos(2x) + \\cos(2y)\\bigr)\\, e^{-4\\nu t}."

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:25
#: 08d9fa745c384a008b4c8e94adf35f51
msgid ""
"The velocity decays exponentially with rate :math:`2\\nu` (twice the "
"kinematic viscosity); the pressure decays at rate :math:`4\\nu`. "
"Substitution verifies that :math:`(u, v, p)` satisfies the incompressible "
"Navier-Stokes equations exactly."
msgstr ""
"速度以速率 :math:`2\\nu`\\ （运动黏度的两倍）指数衰减；压力以速率 :math:`4\\nu` 衰减。代入即可验证 :math:`(u,"
" v, p)` 精确满足不可压缩纳维-斯托克斯方程。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:31
#: 9889eab90d414ad183bf2e67017b12c7
msgid ""
"The script imposes Dirichlet velocities on every boundary node equal to the "
"exact solution at the current time. This sidesteps the need for periodic "
"boundaries and isolates the spatial / temporal discretization error."
msgstr "脚本在每个边界节点上施加等于当前时刻精确解的狄利克雷速度。这样既绕开了对周期性边界的需求，也将空间 / 时间离散误差单独隔离出来。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:38
#: 0a1959b0b5e5470ab935fcabeea9fc35
msgid "Solver"
msgstr "求解器"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:40
#: 81985bb7b61342deb99dd2caa3e5e8a9
msgid ""
"The transient ``NavierStokesTransientAssembler`` from :doc:`cylinder_flow` "
"is reused verbatim — implicit Euler in time, SUPG/PSPG with adaptive "
":math:`\\tau` in space. The only changes are:"
msgstr ""
"来自 :doc:`cylinder_flow` 的瞬态 ``NavierStokesTransientAssembler`` "
"被原样复用——时间上采用隐式欧拉法，空间上采用带自适应 :math:`\\tau` 的 SUPG/PSPG。仅有的改动是："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:45
#: a529e80b94034b219133e4402cb6cbbe
msgid "domain :math:`[0, 2\\pi]^2` instead of the cylinder channel,"
msgstr "计算域为 :math:`[0, 2\\pi]^2`\\ ，而非圆柱通道，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:46
#: 44b990e283e84054b2e4935600a98583
msgid ""
"Dirichlet velocity from the exact solution rather than a parabolic inlet,"
msgstr "狄利克雷速度取自精确解，而非抛物型入口，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:48
#: d2f26fa2f20144ea8a89e5b9f2a91423
msgid ""
"every step writes :math:`L^2` errors against the analytical velocity and "
"pressure to a results file."
msgstr "每一步都将相对于解析速度与压力的 :math:`L^2` 误差写入结果文件。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:51
#: bd827ebbe7a84c038e8ac58d4b5523e1
msgid "examples/fluid/taylor_green/taylor_green.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/fluid/taylor_green/taylor_green.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:71
#: 6a1678355b064ee8b0f0f677c5e84910
msgid "h-convergence"
msgstr "h 收敛性"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:73
#: e427776f3645454e83cb610e59aadb51
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The script sweeps the mesh size :math:`h = 2\\pi / n_\\text{grid}` through a"
" list of values and records the :math:`L^2` velocity and pressure errors at "
"a fixed final time. For P1-P1 elements with SUPG/PSPG one expects:"
msgstr ""
"脚本让网格尺寸 :math:`h = 2\\pi / n_\\text{grid}` 遍历一组取值，并在固定的终止时刻记录 :math:`L^2` "
"速度误差与压力误差。对于带 SUPG/PSPG 的 P1-P1 单元，预期为："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:78
#: 33fba1ccb1374e7ea1cbbd5f9a84fd73
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":math:`\\|\\mathbf{u}_h - \\mathbf{u}\\|_{L^2} = \\mathcal{O}(h^2)`"
msgstr ":math:`\\|\\mathbf{u}_h - \\mathbf{u}\\|_{L^2} = \\mathcal{O}(h^2)`"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:79
#: 537690b6521c420ca152629b76e5af3a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":math:`\\|p_h - p\\|_{L^2} = \\mathcal{O}(h)`"
msgstr ":math:`\\|p_h - p\\|_{L^2} = \\mathcal{O}(h)`"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:81
#: 30ec3d64f3d84863b84001b1a41ddaea
msgid "The console output is a table:"
msgstr "控制台输出为一张表格："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:92
#: 3966e0ec7fc24ad697456f29ed24741f
msgid ""
"(numbers approximate, will vary slightly with the chosen :math:`\\nu` and "
":math:`\\Delta t`). The plot ``taylor_green_convergence.png`` shows the same"
" data on a log-log axis with reference :math:`h^2` and :math:`h^1` slopes."
msgstr ""
"（数值为近似值，会随所选的 :math:`\\nu` 与 :math:`\\Delta t` 略有变化）。图 "
"``taylor_green_convergence.png`` 在对数-对数坐标轴上展示相同数据，并附有参考的 :math:`h^2` 与 "
":math:`h^1` 斜率。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:97
#: 33aabd5ec46b4f16a6a3c35a9d3d2986
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If the observed rates differ from the expected :math:`\\mathcal{O}(h^2)` / "
":math:`\\mathcal{O}(h)`, something in the solver is wrong — most often a "
"subtle bug in the stabilization or in the boundary-condition imposition."
msgstr ""
"如果观测到的收敛阶与预期的 :math:`\\mathcal{O}(h^2)` / :math:`\\mathcal{O}(h)` "
"不符，那么求解器中必有问题——最常见的是稳定化或边界条件施加中的隐蔽 bug。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:104
#: 732bbdc9d2794454b919ee725e0b3971
msgid "Mass-weighted error norm"
msgstr "质量加权误差范数"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:106
#: bf09b5b4f2054c9b9042a381f0e7dcea
msgid "The script computes the discrete :math:`L^2` norm via the mass matrix:"
msgstr "脚本通过质量矩阵计算离散的 :math:`L^2` 范数："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:109
#: a29be2d4cb1a4971925f2488fa07ef17
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\|e_h\\|_{L^2}^2\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"e_h^T\\, M\\, e_h\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\sum_K \\int_K e_h^2 \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"\\|e_h\\|_{L^2}^2\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"e_h^T\\, M\\, e_h\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\sum_K \\int_K e_h^2 \\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:117
#: ccaf8543f955417f8d670d984428ff0d
msgid ""
"assembled by :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler`. This is the right "
"norm for FEM error analysis (it integrates over the elements, weighted by "
"the basis), unlike the simple Euclidean norm of the nodal error vector."
msgstr ""
"其中质量矩阵由 :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler` "
"装配。这是有限元误差分析的正确范数（它在各单元上积分，并以基函数加权），不同于节点误差向量的简单欧几里得范数。"

