msgstr "**``taylor_green.mp4``**\\ （可选）——衰减涡的动画。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:134
#: 546a99d5ba704a058ab1561608217050
msgid ""
"Taylor-Green vortex at t=0.5 — vorticity + streamlines, speed + velocity "
"vectors"
msgstr "t=0.5 时的泰勒-格林涡——涡量＋流线，速度＋速度矢量"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/taylor_green.rst:138
#: df660416bed241aaa74d0da1ff8820cd
msgid ""
"Output of ``taylor_green.py`` at :math:`t=0.5`. Left: vorticity field with "
"overlaid streamlines — the canonical periodic :math:`2\\times2` pattern of "
"alternating-sign vortices. Right: speed magnitude with velocity vectors, "
"showing the characteristic \"saddle\" structure between adjacent rolls. The "
"amplitude has decayed by :math:`\\exp(-2\\nu t)` from the analytical initial"
" condition, which the script's convergence study uses as ground truth."
msgstr ""
"``taylor_green.py`` 在 :math:`t=0.5` 时的输出。左：叠加流线的涡量场——经典的周期性 "
":math:`2\\times2` 交替符号涡阵列。右：带速度矢量的速度大小，展示了相邻卷之间特征性的“鞍”状结构。相对解析初始条件，幅值已衰减了 "
":math:`\\exp(-2\\nu t)`\\ ，脚本的收敛性研究即以此为参考真值。"

